    <item>
      <title>Academic Life &amp; Research</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/about/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/about/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;The Objective&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;the-objective&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span&#xD;&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#the-objective&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Applying mechanical engineering principles and self-directed biomedical research to innovate within aerospace and cross-disciplinary engineering, driven by a commitment to the H.O.L.M.E.S. research initiative.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Academic Foundation &amp;amp; History&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;academic-foundation--history&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span&#xD;&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#academic-foundation--history&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;BSc in Mechanical Engineering&lt;/strong&gt; | &lt;em&gt;IUBAT&lt;/em&gt;&#xA;&lt;em&gt;Expected Graduation: May 2028&lt;/em&gt;&#xA;Currently advancing through my core coursework with a rigorous focus on Advanced Manufacturing, Linear Algebra, Economics, and Electronics. This formal education serves as the physical framework for my broader aerospace and autonomous systems ambitions.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
